  "prompt": "Who is the best broadband service provider in Mysore?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" broadband service provider in Mysore can be subjective and depends on various factors such as internet speed, reliability, customer service, and pricing. As of my last update, some of the popular broadband service providers in Mysore include:\n\n1. **BSNL** - Known for its extensive coverage and various plans.\n2. **Airtel** - Offers high-speed fiber broadband with good customer service.\n3. **JioFiber** - Known for competitive pricing and high-speed plans.\n4. **ACT Fibernet** - Regarded for high-speed internet and reliability, especially in urban areas.\n5. **Hathway** - Offers a range of plans and is popular in certain regions.\n\nTo determine the best provider for your needs, consider checking customer reviews, available plans, speed tests, and service availability in your specific area. You can also consult local forums or social media groups for current user experiences to make a more informed decision.",
